t(Q) \ge 2^{n-2\sqrt{n}}
t(Q) = C_{n-2}
C_{n-2} \ge  2^{n-2\sqrt{n}}
C_{n-2} \gg  2^{n-2\sqrt{n}}
n
\displaystyle \binom{2n}{n}
\displaystyle \frac{4^n}{2n+1}
\displaystyle t(Q) = C_{n-2} = \frac{1}{n-1} \binom{2(n-2)}{n-2} \geq \frac{1}{n-1} \frac{4^{n-2}}{2n - 3} = \frac{2^{n+2\sqrt{n} - 4}}{(n-1)(2n-3)} 2^{n-2\sqrt{n}}
2^{n+2\sqrt{n} - 4} \geq (n-1)(2n-3)
n > 3
C_{3-2} = 1 > 2^{3 - 2\sqrt{3}}
t(Q) \geq 2^{n-2\sqrt{n}}
